						<rdg wit="#Translation">And in Lyonnais Gaul he composed the beginnings of this book</rdg>
					</app>
				</s>
				<s>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">et in gallia belgica consummata est id est in ciuitate que dicitur brigalis</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">and in Belgian Gaul it was completed, that is, in the city that is called Bruges,</rdg>
					</app>
				</s>
